`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Anger
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'anger'

 The spell anger is a spell in the emotions spell group that when cast upon
yourself, increases your damage roll at a cost to your armor class. The length
of time, of course, is dependent on level.

